                     <interp inst="t18520816-780-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, stealing 1 handkerchief, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18520816-name-80" type="victimName">
