                        <interp inst="t18520816-name-82" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN LEONARD</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman</hi>, 621). I produce a certificate from Mr. Clark's office (<hi rend="italic">read—"Lewis Woolfe, convicted Dec, 1850, of stealing a purse and money from the person. 
Confined Three Months the last week solitary.</hi>)"—I was present—the prisoner is the person.</p>
